{"tid":2517675,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony PSN 被曝隱藏條款：跨平台遊戲需支付特許權使用費","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:07:51.000Z","uid":66113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7aafabda8b192652c9b85f058c30d84d54e97d","tid":2517675,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"Epic和蘋果的訴訟案打得火熱，雙方不僅你來我往互甩文件，也有許多其他公司被牽扯進來。<br />\n<br />\n在最新的訴訟文件中，曝光了索尼要求支持跨平台的遊戲開發商支付相應特許權使用費。<br />\n文件示例詳細說明了特許權使用費的運作方式：<br />\n如果玩家選擇在PS4或PS5主機上遊玩跨平台遊戲，但同時又在其他平台進行虛擬貨幣交易<br />\n，那麼索尼就認為PSN平台的資金收入減少，要收取跨平台遊戲開發商一定的特許權使用<br />\n費，具體數額取決於PS主機玩家的總交易額和PSN平台的交易額的差值。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，跨平台遊戲開發商需每月向索尼共享用戶報告，並詳細說明PSN平台的收入份<br />\n額。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.cnbetacdn.com/article/2021/0504/b685c1dd354cb9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.cnbetacdn.com%2Farticle%2F2021%2F0504%2Fb685c1dd354cb9d.jpg&h=ebb70dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXTurSEi2RVZYm87ssGyDLiKtbcq5BFTrXq1ddFqsP4uz?filename=RmY2dcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmY2dcO.jpg&h=468f5aa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05cfaff86435c9b281e30793f069ce9992c334f0","tid":2517675,"uid":252784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54896d71b401e035becc17c4dcc86dd68f2ceda","tid":2517675,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"Sony: 我比你班任豚軟撚外掛PC狗同我班尊貴Sony玩家玩, 但我收唔足課金就要收你廠商錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5145013fcff3332a971f354b6e54ddc3151f6360","tid":2517675,"uid":347211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"留名等索索3子入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992cf05b07eee861cc2539f5ad99e7991ff62c23","tid":2517675,"uid":140714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"隱咩藏條款，根本正常開發商都會知，玩家唔會特登走去睇developers 嘅條款就話隱藏，咁呢個世界都幾多隱藏嘢"}]}